  <scopecontent id="aspace_7ef9f60e6fb3263c5b820e6e006b874c">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>VHS videotapes. Also, includes notebooks that serve as an index to the collection and contain information on title, date, length of video, actors, directors, and description. Photographs from publicity materials are included.</p>  </scopecontent>
  <accessrestrict id="aspace_1fc03c2bd7c2749ea997eb171a9652a4">
    <head>Access Restrictions:</head>
<p>Videotaps restricted to permission of the curator. The notebooks, in boxes 12 and 15, are open for use.</p>  </accessrestrict>
